OL,3,CMan arrested for possession of weapon
OL,4,Cnear Mountbatten-Windsor's home
OL,6,FA man has been arrested near Andrew
OL,7,FMountbatten-Windsor's home, on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of a public order offence
OL,9,Fand possession of an offensive weapon.
OL,11,FPolice say the arrest follows reports
OL,12,Fof a man behaving in an intimidating
OL,13,Fmanner.
OL,15,FIn a statement issued on Thursday,
OL,16,FNorfolk police said: "Officers were
OL,17,Fcalled to Wolferton shortly after
OL,18,F7.30pm yesterday (Wednesday 6 May
OL,19,F2026) following a report a man was
OL,20,Fbehaving in an intimidating manner in
OL,21,Fthe village.
