OL,3,CMan arrested for possession of weapon
OL,4,Cnear Mountbatten-Windsor's home
OL,6,F"Officers attended, and the man was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of a public
OL,8,Forder offence and possession of an
OL,9,Foffensive weapon.
OL,11,F"He was taken to King's Lynn Police
OL,12,FInvestigation Centre for questioning
OL,13,Fand remains in custody."
OL,15,FEarlier, the Telegraph reported that
OL,16,FMountbatten-Windsor had been
OL,17,Fthreatened by a balaclava-clad man
OL,18,Fwhile walking his dogs.
