OL,3,CMan arrested for possession of weapon
OL,4,Cnear Mountbatten-Windsor's home
OL,6,FThe man had been sitting in a car near
OL,7,Fthe Sandringham Estate in Norfolk,
OL,8,Fwaiting for Andrew, the newspaper said.
